e, led to accumulation of metabolites that may be characteristic for plant stress responses like systemic acquired resistance. Evaluation of the  in vivo  function of the different CYP94-enzymes on the JA-sensitivity demonstrated that particularly CYP94B-enzymes might play an essential role for JA-response, whereas CYP94C1 might only be of minor importance.},
